    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class is an alternative to directly invoking <ref refid="group__GeneralGroup_1ga7cfd6d2c7fdde75ec5577e2e10511787" kindref="member">meshToDirectionVolume</ref> for the mesh retrieved from the teeth mask. It is better because when a single mesh is created from mask, some neighboring teeth might fuse together, creating incorrect mask. This class invokes meshing for each teeth separately, thus eliminating this problem. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
